  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e1316ff5826be665f05a1dd65a4a6f4e.poster.avif?t=1727254288\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e1316ff5826be665f05a1dd65a4a6f4e.webm?t=1727254288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e1316ff5826be665f05a1dd65a4a6f4e.mp4?t=1727254288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are a time traveller lost in time, and must jump your way through history, where you balance on pillars, lamp posts, trees, and many other objects in order to reach the time portal and continue your journey. Assume local disguises to avoid suspicion.<br><br>The platforms are loose and fall over from your weight so you have to keep your balance and measure your next jump.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e4291fade809e4e59009daccb5fe8181.poster.avif?t=1727254288\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e4291fade809e4e59009daccb5fe8181.webm?t=1727254288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e4291fade809e4e59009daccb5fe8181.mp4?t=1727254288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock beautiful locations from different time periods and parts of the globe, and collect pixelart characters on your way, from location specific Vikings and Samurai, to slightly less historically accurate gorillas, dolls and smartly dressed foxes!<br><br>Don't fall down... but if you do, just <strong>Git Up!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e1316ff5826be665f05a1dd65a4a6f4e.poster.avif?t=1727254288\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e1316ff5826be665f05a1dd65a4a6f4e.webm?t=1727254288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e1316ff5826be665f05a1dd65a4a6f4e.mp4?t=1727254288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are a time traveller lost in time, and must jump your way through history, where you balance on pillars, lamp posts, trees, and many other objects in order to reach the time portal and continue your journey. Assume local disguises to avoid suspicion.<br><br>The platforms are loose and fall over from your weight so you have to keep your balance and measure your next jump.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e4291fade809e4e59009daccb5fe8181.poster.avif?t=1727254288\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e4291fade809e4e59009daccb5fe8181.webm?t=1727254288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913920/extras/e4291fade809e4e59009daccb5fe8181.mp4?t=1727254288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock beautiful locations from different time periods and parts of the globe, and collect pixelart characters on your way, from location specific Vikings and Samurai, to slightly less historically accurate gorillas, dolls and smartly dressed foxes!<br><br>Don't fall down... but if you do, just <strong>Git Up!</strong>",
